r1_2 is active
r2_2 is idle
c0_2 is busy
b0_2 is low
@200
r0_2 is active
r1_2 is idle
r2_2 is active
c0_2 is busy
b0_2 is high
@300
r0_2 is idle
r1_2 is active
r2_2 is idle
c0_2 is free
b0_2 is low

@enduml
